  <span id="freeText9011286728586929139" style="display:none">Well written and thought provoking, Cracked raises some very interesting questions about the DSM, although the venture into the pharmaceutical industry's role in psychiatry was spotted a mile away (Bad Pharma by Ben Goldacre for further reading if anyone wants to). </span>
