<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51070251-early"><img alt="Early: An Intimate History of Premature Birth and What It Teaches Us About Being Human" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1565339480l/51070251._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
